{"tid":2458451,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV《最後一屆口罩小姐》首播 網民大讚節目搞笑193轉數快","createTime":"2021-03-23T12:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T15:25:05.000Z","uid":350584,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c0bafbc433869a688d1e529d1296424001cc34","tid":2458451,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"喺新冠肺炎疫情下，口罩成為大家嘅生活必需品，所以ViuTV就舉辦另類選美真人騷《最後一屆口罩小姐》。節目早前已經宣布口罩小姐40強名單，並公開候選佳麗們嘅相片和資料。去到噚晚，節目終於出街啦！而家就同大家睇下網民有啲咩反應啦！<br />\n<br />\n《最後一屆口罩小姐》由ERROR四位成員擔任主持，噚晚ERROR四子一開始先周街搵靚女，然後先返錄影廠甄選出20強。參加者們就要喺佢哋面前進行才藝表演，然後佢哋可以揀選5位參加者進入加入自己嘅組別。喺噚晚，四位主持嘅表現以193最令網民滿意，仲紛紛留言大讚佢，例如：「193 真係不得了」、「193 carry 哂啲節奏」、「笑死33反應好快」、「193轉數快又搞笑」及「佢綜藝加主持能力一流」，而另一主持保錡就得唔到網民歡心，除咗不停望電話之外，佢仲猴擒上台搶人，網民睇完都留言話佢係敗筆，例如「好心幫poki打格仔啦」、「節目敗筆：保錡」、「又話雪佢？點解仲見到佢？」、「保錡扮曬大老」、「有保錡嘅&hellip;」及「呢節冇咗poki鏡頭即刻好睇晒」等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/q2BwPfNnVriBW8hzH.zjxQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtoPTY2Ng--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/779dbcb0-8b9b-11eb-bb6d-7e7a91432ace\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fq2BwPfNnVriBW8hzH.zjxQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtoPTY2Ng--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-03%2F779dbcb0-8b9b-11eb-bb6d-7e7a91432ace&h=43f9b070&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbc3657f413a734379510fd6e6a5cbc0c1ad18f1","tid":2458451,"uid":350584,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/glNlUCJa4wgbwQtyWlTDAw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtoPTY2Ng--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-03/3d021330-8b9b-11eb-9bbc-7ba0c8482f47\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FglNlUCJa4wgbwQtyWlTDAw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlna